body:
Shenanigans with Avengers Glasses

I work in a place that sells glasses, and there’s a section of kids frames that are branded and theres a few there that are Avengers branded. Some of the things I get up to:

1. Merchandising

Co-worker: ok so we have to place the princess glasses here like so

Me: Yup. Agreed

Co-Worker: Minions here

Me: ok

Co-Worker: And the Avengers ones like

Me: NO!

Me: *proceeds to allign Captain America and Iron Man glasses together and then Hulk and Thor together*

Me: Husbands stay together!

Me: *places Spiderman glasses under Iron Man ones* and with his father

Co-Worker: ………wft?….I mean ok I guess it looks asthetically pleasing

Me: Damn straight. I know what I’m doing


2. Throwing hands with children

Me: Ok kiddo which glasses do you want? Do you like Jurassic Park? You like the Minions? Star Wars? Avengers?

Kid: Yeah I like those!

Me: Cool me too! Let’s try some on! Whose your favorite Avenger?

Kid: Spiderman is the best!

Me: *struggling not to cry* he sure is! What about Iron Man? You like him?

Kid: No I don’t really like him

Me: …………you fuckin take that back right now you little shi-


3. Packing away

Co-Worker: I need a green case

Other co-worker: here you go

Co-worker: a kids one too

Co-worker: which colour you reckon we should put the Spiderman ones in?

Me: black like the ashes he turned into

Co-workers: abBY nO!!!!

summary: So brace yourself for this question I asked my friends but no one could answer me
body:
So brace yourself for this question I asked my friends but no one could answer me

So when a starfish loses an arm, the body grows another arm and the arm grows another body, right, sorted.

When deadpool gets something cut off, it grows back but the part that was cut off doesn’t do anything.

So if deadpool got his head cut off, would his head grow another body, or would his body grow another head?

Because the body:head ratio is greater so his body should just grow another head, however dude that’s his head, like he cant just grow another brain???
